  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2489970/extras/8c1211a260eec91f50bd6919bb9241fc.poster.avif?t=1723867390\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2489970/extras/8c1211a260eec91f50bd6919bb9241fc.webm?t=1723867390\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2489970/extras/8c1211a260eec91f50bd6919bb9241fc.mp4?t=1723867390\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Speard is a 3D Fast Paced Platformer, the objective is to go fast! <br><br>Run fast with the help of your <strong>Spear</strong> that gives you a forward thrust and <strong>explosive knives</strong> that you throw to rocket jump.<br><br>Explore vibrant area's parkouring your way through each level, with each area giving a new twist to the game!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2489970/extras/ec753a21dc5a6e271b98e686986cdf4b.poster.avif?t=1723867390\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2489970/extras/ec753a21dc5a6e271b98e686986cdf4b.webm?t=1723867390\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2489970/extras/ec753a21dc5a6e271b98e686986cdf4b.mp4?t=1723867390\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
